## Key Architecture
- App Router with `src/` directory
- `src/components/` — reusable UI components
- `src/lib/` — utilities, helpers, API clients
- `src/hooks/` — custom React hooks
- `src/types/` — TypeScript interfaces
- `src/data/` — mock data, constants

